*
         * @directive v-focus
         * @param {Boolean} doFocus
         * @description
         *   Focuses the element when it is inserted in the DOM, provided that it is bound to a true value.

*
         * @prop {Boolean} autoFocus
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Whether the component should be auto focused or not.
Manually focus the form field every time the prop is mutated.

*
         * @method
         * @public
         * @name focus
         * @description
         *   Focuses the form field. You probably want to override this method to something more suitable.
